citation.excerpt: This is the GitHub repo for our paper "P2: A Plan-and-Pretrain Approach for Knowledge Graph-to-Text Generation" by Qipeng Guo, Zhijing Jin, Ning Dai, Xipeng Qiu, Xiangyang Xue, David Wipf, and Zheng Zhang.

description.excerpt:
Our P2 model consists of two steps:
- Planner by relational graph convolutional networks ([Zhao et al, 2020](https://www.aclweb.org/anthology/2020.acl-main.224/))
- Pretrained Seq2Seq model: T5 ([Raffel et al., 2020](https://arxiv.org/abs/1910.10683))
![](https://i.imgur.com/hJEQzPx.png)

This is the GitHub repo for our paper "P2: A Plan-and-Pretrain Approach for Knowledge Graph-to-Text Generation" by Qipeng Guo, Zhijing Jin, Ning Dai, Xipeng Qiu, Xiangyang Xue, David Wipf, and Zheng Zhang.  
Our model achieves the top #1 performance at the English track of the WebNLG 2020 Challenge at INLG 2020 Workshop.

invocation.excerpt: Our model output on WebNLG 2020 test set is available at output.txt.
